        <updateDate>2019-09-03T21:02:04Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Promoting Responsible and Free Trade Act </b></p> <p>This bill allows for congressional disapproval of certain trade actions, including actions by the Office of the U.S. Trade Representative. Congressional approval is required for a trade adjustment for national security reasons. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
